event.title: was seen as a "beautiful prospect" by the gazeteer in 1838

data.event: The City of Prospect was named as such because it area was seen as a "beautiful prospect" by the gazeteer in 1838.
In 1944 the city council voted to adopt the same name for the suburb of Prospect.
